+ AddButtonStyle 2 Inactive pixmap buttons/grayglass_max.xpm
+ AddButtonStyle 3 Active pixmap buttons/redglass_close.xpm
+ AddButtonStyle 3 Inactive pixmap buttons/grayglass_close.xpm
